    {
      "text": "brukt om to (personer, ting, begreper) for å uttrykke at de er omtalt sammen, eller at de naturlig hører sammen",
      "translation": "used about two (people, things, concepts) to express that they are mentioned together, that they naturally belong together",
      "examples": [
        "begge foreldrene",
        "ha vondt i begge armene",
